1 NAME Percival William /House/
2 GIVN Percival William
2 SURN House
1 SEX M
1 BIRT
2 DATE 9 DEC 1883
2 PLAC Chaffey Township, Muskoka, Ontario Canada
2 NOTE (Foster Child) Unknown father. Mother Catherine (Kate) Jordan
1 DEAT Y
2 DATE 7 JUN 1968
2 PLAC Huntsville Memorial Hospital, Huntsville, Ontario, Canada
2 AGE 84
1 FAMS @F500159@
1 FAMC @F500161@
