>>Locator note: This tract was located at the mouth
2 CONC  of Paines Run, on the South River, 4 miles south of current-day Grottoes, Rockingham, VA.  To clarify, Grottoes is on the Rockingham-Augusta county line, and the Trout farm was located in Augusta Cou
2 CONC nty.  In more exact terms, the mouth of Paines Run is located at N 38 degrees 12' 37.2 ", W 78 degrees 50' 3.5",  USGS 7.5' Crimora, VA quad (NAD27).  Site first visited in October, 1999.

