1 NOTE <p><p>Husband of <strong>Barbara Eva MILLER</strong> (1792-1856)<br /><br /><strong><a href="http://wc.rootsweb.com/cgi-bin/igm.cgi?op=GET&amp;db=chtrout&amp;id=I04920" target="_new">Wintle TROUT, III
2 CONC </a></strong> was born 20 Feb 1787 in Strasburg, Lancaster, PA, the son of Wendel TROUT II (1743-1820) and Elizabet DRUCKENBROD (1765-1825).<br /><br />Wintle, sometimes spelled "Wendel" or "Vintel", 
2 CONC was married to Barbara Eva MILLER on 13 Apr 1809 in York County, PA. At least 12 children were born to this union.<br /><br />Wintle was the grandson of the immigrant Johann Wendel Georg TRAUT (1689-1
2 CONC 760)</p></p><p><p>Children:</p></p><p><p>Barbara Eva Trout 1809 &ndash; 1884</p></p><p><p>Adam Henry Trout 1811 &ndash; 1890</p></p><p><p>Abraham Trout 1813 &ndash; 1893</p></p><p><p>Samuel Trout 1816
