1 NOTE <p>Obit. gives name as Buleak. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>   Buleak the oldest child of Mr and Mrs William Ludlow, died of </p><p>imflammation of the heart last Wednesday night at 8:30  The remains were </p>
2 CONC <p>interred in New River,  Mr. Durr officiating.  The bereaved parents have </p><p>the sympathy of the entire community.</p><p>                         Rejoice that she has gained it</p><p>           
2 CONC               That bright and glorious home</p><p>                         Where the light of an eternal day</p>                         Beams ever around God's throne.
