2 CONC ne </p></p><p><p></p></p><p><p></p></p><p><p>I have done some research in my library genealogy</p></p><p><p>dept and have posted some records on the John Gearhart,Sr</p></p><p><p>descendants in Miami 
2 CONC Co.Ohio.</p></p><p><p>This John Gearhart,Sr lived in Shenendoah Co.-</p></p><p><p>Rockbridge Co.VA after his death his wife Catherine</p></p><p><p>Cartrought and her children migrated to Miami Co.Ohio
2 CONC .</p></p><p><p>My family legends of four brothers departing from</p></p><p><p>North Carolina,one brother to Ky,one to Ohio,</p></p><p><p>one to Arkansas and one went west never heard from</p></p><p><p
