1 NOTE <p>Samuel was 16 when he was baptized in St. John's Lutheran Church in Abbottstown.</p><p><p></p></p><p><p>A copy of Sam's will is in my documentation.  Samuel left everything to his wife, Catherine. 
2 CONC  His son, Sam, was executor.</p></p><p><p></p></p><p><p>Samuel was a trustee of St. John's Lutheran Church when the current church was completed in 1890.</p></p><p>RIN: MH:N201</p>
